E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%8C%E5%8F%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E6%9C%88%E7%BB%8F%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%89%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%8C%E5%8F%A3%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#月经期间到底有没有忌口#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;其实，经期没这么多忌口，只要吃了没有不舒服，那就能吃&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[doge]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;。那&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9C%88%E7%BB%8F%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%96%9D%E8%8C%B6%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E6%9C%88%E7%BB%8F%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%96%9D%E8%8C%B6%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#月经期间到底能不能喝茶#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;？也能，但最好少喝。茶叶中鞣酸浓度高，含量约有50%，它会影响女性在月经期间的铁质吸收，降低铁质的吸收率，也可能会加重生理期的不适症状。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫来辟谣#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（健康广东） &lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpax6j4e1cj20c60bujs6.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/OcnSlopRx</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/OcnSlopRx</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 01:36:41 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>[吃惊]#过度节食当心饿出脂肪肝# 有些人节食减肥控制体重，肝却已经“胖”到爆表！摄入减少会导致脂肪代谢所需要的活性氧化酶等缺乏，导致脂肪不能代谢，在肝脏...</title><description>&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[吃惊]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%87%E5%BA%A6%E8%8A%82%E9%A3%9F%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%E9%A5%BF%E5%87%BA%E8%84%82%E8%82%AA%E8%82%9D%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%87%E5%BA%A6%E8%8A%82%E9%A3%9F%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%E9%A5%BF%E5%87%BA%E8%84%82%E8%82%AA%E8%82%9D%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#过度节食当心饿出脂肪肝#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 有些人节食减肥控制体重，肝却已经“胖”到爆表！&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;摄入减少会导致脂肪代谢所需要的活性氧化酶等缺乏，导致脂肪不能代谢，在肝脏内大量沉积，形成脂肪肝。&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[话筒]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;卫子提醒：大家一定要坚持科学减肥，管住嘴，迈开腿！除了节食减肥，这原因也会造成脂肪肝👇🏻&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫来辟谣#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（央视新闻）&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpav6cha5wj20m823y7qo.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpav6cm1tgj20m820wx1p.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpav6drsawj20m8235kfk.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpav6dzf7vj20m8271e4b.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpav6awu0kj20m820h1de.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpav6fgmodj20m82s07wh.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpav6faq6wj20m82ix4qp.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpav6e3rc4j20m82bdtyk.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpav68refmj20m81ahk6z.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/OcnqdFfZj</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/OcnqdFfZj</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 00:27:24 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>体外射没事的？？不要抱有侥幸心理。[doge]即使精子排到体外，还是有可能顺着外阴分泌物，悄咪咪流入阴道。而且1滴精液，也包含着大约5万颗精子，每一颗精子都有...</title><description>体外射没事的？？&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;不要抱有侥幸心理。&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[doge]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;即使精子排到体外，还是有可能顺着外阴分泌物，悄咪咪流入阴道。而且1滴精液，也包含着大约5万颗精子，每一颗精子都有可能是“潜力股”，所以我劝你别赌，还是乖乖做好安全措施吧&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[报税]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/0f/2022_baoshui_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫来辟谣#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（深圳市妇幼保健院）&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;假期也不要熬夜，早点睡&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[月亮]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/w_yueliang-ec756dd13a.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpaat6s6pyj20m80j4gpm.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/OciOb6wFq</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/OciOb6wFq</guid><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:42:41 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>五一假期外出，收好#五一假期出行健康提示#[看书]👇🏻①出行时需预防诺如病毒肠炎、食物中毒等食源性疾病；②小朋友需预防百日咳、手足口病；③#郊游时需预...</title><description>五一假期外出，收好&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%80%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%80%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#五一假期出行健康提示#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[看书]&quot; src=&quot;https://fa