rrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hp9w6rzufoj20gc1ffaes.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hp9w6t1nhrj20gc1zlqaf.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/OcfuR5n7q</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/OcfuR5n7q</guid><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 04:16:50 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item></channel></rss>